title: Issaquah Dance Theatre offers free dance class Oct. 30
text:
Browse > Home / A & E / Issaquah Dance Theatre offers free dance class Oct. 30 Issaquah Dance Theatre offers free dance class Oct. 30 
October 16, 2015 
NEW — 3:03 p.m. Oct. 16, 2015 
Issaquah Dance Theatre’s annual free Trick-or-Treat and Dance Class returns Friday, Oct. 30. 
There will be fun activities before and after class, including: 9-9:15 a.m. — Treat decorating 10-10:45 a.m. — Halloween dance party 
Trick-or-treating will take place in the theater’s building following the dance class. 
All ages are welcome. Be sure to wear a costume. 
Learn more by emailing info@idt.comcastbiz.net or calling 391-2632.
